../classes/highscoresupdater.class.php
* dynamically set execution time limit to expire before next highscores update
* retry highscores data download from tibiame.com every 30 sec for a maximum of 10 attempts

../core.php
* curl_get_contents() will return false if server responds with codes 403, 404, 500, 502 or 503

../classes/TibiameComParser.class.php
* check if curl_get_contents() returned false

